{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 232952,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっはっはっ、ええんよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ahahaha, it's fine."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232953,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ここまで含めていつもの恒例行事やから。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Including all this, it’s just the usual annual event."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232954,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　乱義がもらわんことも含めてな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That even includes Ran-gi not getting anything.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232955,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はあ、面倒臭ぇ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haa, this is such a hassle...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232956,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232957,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「コパンドン様、そろそろ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lord Kopandon, it's about time...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232958,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「とっ、もう時間切れかい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, is the time already up?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232959,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほな、ウチそろそろ行くわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, I’ll be heading off soon.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232960,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、Mランドの施設、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, the facilities at M Land,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232961,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　全部まるごと好きに使うてくれてええよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "you can freely use all of them as you like."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232962,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　話はもう通しといたから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I've already taken care of the arrangements for you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232963,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほな、またなー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, see you again.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232964,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232965,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　　＜ばひゅーん！＞",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "  <Vroooom!>"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232966,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "コパンドンの乗り込んだうし車が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The ox-cart that Kopandon boarded"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232967,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "高速で去って行った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "sped away at high speed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232968,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232969,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「嵐みたいな人だったな……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That was a person like a storm..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232970,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　さすが噂のコパ帝国総帥……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As expected from the famed Supreme Commander of the Kopandon Empire...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232971,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あなた達はコパンドンの厚意に甘え、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You all took advantage of Kopandon's kindness,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232972,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "Mランド内のレストランで昼食を頂く。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and enjoyed lunch at a restaurant inside M Land."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232973,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そしてその後、一部メンバー",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then afterwards, some members"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232974,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（主に長田君、ナギ、レリコフ、ヒーロー等）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(mainly Osada-kun, Nagi, Lericov, Hero, etc.)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232975,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "の、強い希望によりMランドで遊ぶこととなった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "decided, at their strong request, to play around at M Land."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232976,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "........"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232977,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232978,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "楽しい時はあっという間に過ぎ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Fun times pass in the blink of an eye,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232979,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あなた達は園内のホテルへ引き上げる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and you all returned to the hotel inside the park."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232980,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一同はあなたの部屋に集まり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Everyone gathered in your room,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232981,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "作戦会議を行った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and held a strategy meeting."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232982,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さて、説明してないことが多かったから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, since there were many things not yet explained,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232983,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　改めて、今の内に説明しておこうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "let me explain them properly now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232984,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はーい、授業を始めるから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, class is starting,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232985,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　おねむの子もちゃんと起きててねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so those feeling sleepy, wake up properly!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232986,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……起きててね？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Stay awake, okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232987,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う、うぃーっす……起きてます……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yeah... I'm awake...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232988,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あははは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ahahaha..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232989,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　昼間ちょっとはしゃぎすぎたねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You guys got a bit too excited during the day, huh.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232990,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すやすや……すぴすぴ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"*sleeping sounds*...*snoring sounds*...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232991,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はいはい、深根ちゃん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, alright, Fukane-chan,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232992,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　起きてーでござる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "wake up, please.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232993,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほらほら、レリコフも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Come on, come on, Lericov too,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232994,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　起きてないと怒られちゃうよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "if you don’t wake up, you’ll get scolded.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232995,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うーーーん……ねむい……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Uuunn... so sleepy...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232996,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほんじゃ先生、しつもーん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, teacher, I have a question.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232997,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい、ナギちゃん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, Nagi-chan?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232998,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えーと、さっき変なこと言ってたけど、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Uh, you said something strange earlier, but,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232999,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔剣カオスを手に入れるには",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "to obtain the Demon Sword Chaos,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233000,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　闘神大会に出る必要があるの？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is it necessary to participate in the Fighting God Tournament?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233001,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うん、そういうこと。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, that’s right."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233002,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　全員でなくともいいけどね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Not everyone has to enter, though.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233003,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まず、魔剣カオスの所在について話しておこうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"First, let’s talk about the whereabouts of the Demon Sword Chaos.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233004,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔剣カオスとは今＜エール＞が持っている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The Demon Sword Chaos is, like the Holy Sword Nikkou which <Ale> currently possesses,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233005,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　聖刀日光と同じく、この世で唯一",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "one of the only weapons in this world"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233006,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人、魔王に対抗できる武器のこと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "that can counter demons and demon lords.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233007,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「既に聖刀日光を擁しているとは言え……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even though we already wield the Holy Sword Nikkou..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233008,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王に対抗する武器は一つでも多い方がいい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it’s better to have as many weapons to oppose the Demon Lord as possible."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233009,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　出来れば魔剣カオスも手に入れたいね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If possible, we want to get the Demon Sword Chaos as well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233010,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、私も賛成です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, I agree as well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233011,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「元々は私達のお父さん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Originally, our father,"
    }
  ]
}

